/*
Argument 0: Sprite
Argument 1: Sprite Index
Argument 2-3: X and Y
Argument 4: Stretch
Argument 5: Stretch Type
    0: X
    1: Y
    2: Both
Argument 6-7: Alignment (uses font variables)
*/
draw_spr_stretch_ext_scr(argument0,argument1,argument2,argument3,argument4,argument5,argument6,argument7,0,c_white,1);